+# Modular Plotting System Architecture
+
+## Overview
+This document describes the modular architecture for the plotting system, separating concerns into distinct layers to improve maintainability and extensibility.
+
+## Architecture Layers
+
+### 1. Model Layer
+Handles data representation and state management.
+
+**Components:**
+- `PlotModel` - Base model for plot data
+- `CombinedPlotModel` - Specialized model for combined plots
+- `PlotDataModel` - Represents individual plot data series
+
+### 2. View Layer
+Manages UI rendering and widget integration.
+
+**Components:**
+- `PlotView` - Main view component for plots
+- `CombinedPlotView` - Specialized view for combined plots
+- `PlotWidget` - Widget integration layer
+
+### 3. Scope Layer
+Controls visualization rendering and interactions.
+
+**Components:**
+- `PlotScope` - Base scope for individual plots
+- `CombinedPlotScope` - Scope for combined plots
+- `PlotRenderer` - Responsible for rendering plot elements
+- `PlotInteractions` - Handles user interactions
+
+### 4. Utility Layer
+Provides helper functions and utilities.
+
+**Components:**
+- `PlotUtils` - General utility functions
+- `PlotConverter` - Data conversion utilities
+- `PlotFormatter` - Data formatting utilities
+- `PlotSanitizer` - Sanitization utilities
+
+### 5. Formatter Layer
+Handles data transformation and standardization.
+
+**Components:**
+- `PlotDataFormatter` - Formats raw data for plotting
+- `CombinedPlotFormatter` - Specialized formatter for combined plots
+- `AxisFormatter` - Handles axis formatting
+
+## Separation of Concerns
+
+### Model Layer
+- Data representation
+- State management
+- Serialization/deserialization
+- Validation
+
+### View Layer
+- UI rendering
+- Widget integration
+- Event handling
+- Lifecycle management
+
+### Scope Layer
+- Visualization rendering
+- Interaction handling
+- Layout calculation
+- Animation and transitions
+
+### Utility Layer
+- Helper functions
+- Data manipulation
+- Configuration utilities
+- Constants and enums
+
+### Formatter Layer
+- Data transformation
+- Standardization
+- Type conversion
